---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="Aerospace engineering student at Rutgers University, interning at AlphaWave."
	pubDate={new Date('June 04 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		I'm Rohan Yadalla — an aerospace engineering student at Rutgers University finishing my final
		semester in December 2026. I'm based in Monroe Township, NJ.
	</p>

	<p>
		This summer I'm interning at <strong>AlphaWave</strong>, a healthcare AI startup, where I'm
		building AI-powered tools for physician practices. My work spans full-stack development,
		automation pipelines, and applying engineering systems thinking to healthcare software.
	</p>

	<p>
		My academic background is in aerodynamics, flight dynamics, compressible flow, and aerospace
		materials. I'm interested in the intersection of autonomy, aerospace systems, and the software
		that ties them together — particularly where AI is starting to reshape how both fields operate.
	</p>

	<p>
		This blog is where I write about aerospace engineering concepts, the projects I'm working on,
		and the ideas I'm turning over. If something I wrote was useful or you want to connect, find me
		on <a href="https://github.com/RohYada">GitHub</a> or <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/rohan-yadalla">LinkedIn</a>.
	</p>
</Layout>
